<content type="html" xml:base="http://forums.nesdev.com/viewtopic.php?t=872&amp;p=7731#p7731"><![CDATA[
That's exactly what I'm planning to do with my CNRAM cart (for use with CopyNES) - connect the outer pins on your switch to PPU A10 and PPU A11 and connect the center pin to VRAM A10, and you should be all set.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=7">Quietust</a> — Tue Dec 27, 2005 3:25 pm</p><hr />
